item.title: End WA-125 North at WA-124
item.description: End WA-125 North at WA-124. Turn right for WA-124 east to Waitsburg and Prescott. Turn left for WA-124 west to Pasco.

item.title: US-12 West at WA-124
item.description: US-12 west at WA-124. Continue ahead for WA-124 west to Prescott. Turn left for US-12 west to Walla Walla.

item.title: US-12 West Approaching WA-124
item.description: US-12 west approaching WA-124 junction in Waitsburg. Turn left at intersection with WA-124 to continue west on US-12 towards Walla Walla.
